videos.description: Iowa QB C.J. Beathard throws a deep pass that is intercepted by Minnesota DB KiAnte Hardin.

videos.headline: Wadley's 54-yard TD gives Iowa late lead
videos.description: Akrum Wadley breaks free for a 54-yard touchdown, Iowa's first of the game, to give the Hawkeyes a 14-7 lead over Minnesota after the two-point conversion.

videos.headline: L. Daniels Jr. Run For Two-point Conversion
videos.description: L. Daniels Jr. Run For Two-point Conversion

videos.headline: Smith makes great grab by the sideline
videos.description: Driving late in the fourth quarter, Minnesota quarterback Mitch Leidner finds Brian Smith who makes the sweet grab down the sideline for a 23-yard gain that puts the Gophers in the red zone down seven against Iowa.
